### Variables
@baseUrl = https://qjfygjtondljywhbqbfj.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Récupérer tous les services actifs (cas nominal)
GET {{baseUrl}}/services-get-services
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 2 - Filtrer par type de service
GET {{baseUrl}}/services-get-services?service_type=traiteur
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 3 - Récupérer tous les services (actifs et inactifs)
GET {{baseUrl}}/services-get-services?is_active=false
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 4 - Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/services-get-services?page=2&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 5 - Combinaison de filtres
GET {{baseUrl}}/services-get-services?service_type=decoration&is_active=true&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

